{"word":"λυτήρ","slug":"λυτήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λυτήρ</b></el> <el>(λῠτήρ, ῆρος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λύω'><el>λύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one who looses, a deliverer</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an arbitrator, decider</i>, <el>νεικέων</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}